data.description: Beautiful home in Riverside Terrace. Floor plan offers great flow for entertaining and comfortable daily living. Crown molding, ample storage throughout and original hardwood floors!  The only carpet in the house is on the stairs leading up to the private primary suite. Large, private backyard is perfect for entertaining and backyard BBQs. Wonderful place to call home!  Refrigerator, Washer and Dryer stay with the house.  Roof 2023* New Deck 2023* Additional Insulation 2022* New AC Condenser 2022  and much more. Residents of this community enjoy easy access to major freeway systems, world renowned medical care, Houston's finest museums, restaurants and so much more.  Measurements are approximate.  Buyer to verify school eligibility. - Info Per Seller
